Summary

We can roughly see that in those 11 years, protective measures, public buildings, roads and Bridges suffered the most damage in the hurricanes.Between 2009 and 2019, New York suffered the most hurricanes, accounting for 17% of the countrys total. The second is Florida and New jersey.

Meanwhile We can find that the cities that are hardest hit by hurricanes are those on the east coast, and they receive more aid each year.
